      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help but it just feels like they don't get it. they say \"it gets better\" but it's just been months and the house is still so empty. i feel like i'm just existing, not living. there's no point in trying to move on when the only thing that made life feel real is gone. it just feels like a constant, heavy weight on my chest that won't let me breathe.",
